title: FSX P3D F1 GTN 750 650 cycle 1412 update
description:
So this will update your Flight1 Garmin GTN 750 and 650 to the current cycle of 1412.

To install follow these instructions.

Go to:

C:ProgramDataGarminGTN Trainerdb

There is a file there named AVTN_WW_DB.bin...

I RECOMMEND YOU BACK UP THE ORIGINAL FIRST.... Example - This can be done by renaming it to something like AVTN_WW_DB_BAK1412 or whatever the current cycle is.

Then simply place the above file in the folder or overwrite the current one if you choose.

BANG your on cycle 1412 on both GTN 750 and 650. 

FSXSTUFF4U
